      "content": "That's not helpful. You're just repeating the noise I just told you I was tired of seeing. If I walk into that boardroom and tell them the situation is a \"ticking time bomb,\" they're going to pull our funding and shut the whole regional operation down.\n\nI'm not asking for a weather report. I'm asking you to look at the underlying structural data. Is there a way to frame this with a high confidence level of stability? I need something I can actually use to keep this project moving. Can we justify a high-confidence stability rating based on the long-term trends?",
